{"tid":704981,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"可唔可以唔好再將張敬軒同張國榮比？","createTime":"2018-06-16T17:43:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-17T07:27:26.000Z","uid":49018,"like":57,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"1ff21d6270adc3dc62f6265ca704c64b119bad60","tid":704981,"uid":49018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T17:43:41.000Z","msg":"雖則我對張敬軒場Show冇乜意見<br />\n人地講到明係降兩度<br />\n但係觀眾想睇佢正正常常咁唱<br />\n又唔係唔合理<br />\n但係係唔同嘅post都見到<br />\n有啲低能將佢同張國榮比<br />\n即刻無名火起 係咪連登用戶太後生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n1.張國榮係2000年熱情演唱會<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">從未扮過女人</span><br />\n試問聲<br />\n你有冇見過人扮女人留鬚呀撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/17/013615_bd6c16f996e004f55967b5874a1bec2f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F17%2F013615_bd6c16f996e004f55967b5874a1bec2f.png&h=1afaf7be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.兩個演唱會本質根本唔同<br />\n降兩度單純以女性打扮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係熱情演唱會係搵左法國設計師<br />\nJean Paul Gaultier，而當中嘅概念係<br />\n「from angel to devil」配合演唱會嘅<br />\nrundown同埋服裝的演變<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/17/013841_a5f451c45b76963d209bc6acc1cf107b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F17%2F013841_a5f451c45b76963d209bc6acc1cf107b.png&h=183f4e39&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n完全係兩個層次 <br />\n張國榮本來可以將<br />\n香港嘅演唱會提升一個層次<br />\n可以香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n張敬軒嗰show<br />\n點樣可以拎黎比<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過有一點係冇錯<br />\n香港人十八年黎係完全冇進步過<br />\n老實講見到鄰post有過千正皮<br />\n心都寒一寒<br />\n好難怪香港唔會再有天王巨星<br />\n條片張國榮自己都反擊過一啲<br />\n極度膚淺嘅人 正皮過鄰post嘅麻煩睇睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/HDgZcAfrgW4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FHDgZcAfrgW4&d=SN79dnOdyUqSvXT8OLBezf1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=5b463565\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/HDgZcAfrgW4</a>"},{"pid":"ed1eb7df3c007fb107b324e624b41edae2e11193","tid":704981,"uid":182286,"like":5,"dislike":11,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T17:46:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"46fc87a5f99634faed6680a50c49fd04c5fa4aa6","tid":704981,"uid":49018,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"ed1eb7df3c007fb107b324e624b41edae2e11193","tid":704981,"uid":182286,"like":5,"dislike":11,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T17:46:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T17:58:40.000Z","msg":"其實唔係想批判張敬軒<br />\n我覺得佢唱歌係而家香港黎講已經數一數二<br />\n但係見到啲低能拎佢同張國榮比<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要知一半唔知一半<br />\n仲要自稱鍾意張國榮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9a496381ef14c10afd5dc9def07e4b68d60db3c","tid":704981,"uid":49018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T17:59:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>兩個都係姓張 差天共地</blockquote>其實唔係想批評張敬軒<br />\n我覺得佢唱歌係而家香港黎講已經數一數二<br />\n但係見到啲低能拎佢同張國榮比<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要知一半唔知一半<br />\n仲要自稱鍾意張國榮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"5379cd9bbfa8f0d0a5114741e7062545978ae787","tid":704981,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T18:07:27.000Z","msg":"你有冇見過人扮女人留鬚<br />\n<br />\n吳孟達"},{"pid":"9e66f94010d05fe16e3192fb32b3dbfde76d974e","tid":704981,"uid":49018,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"5379cd9bbfa8f0d0a5114741e7062545978ae787","tid":704981,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T18:07:27.000Z","msg":"你有冇見過人扮女人留鬚<br />\n<br />\n吳孟達"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T18:11:59.000Z","msg":"我意思係<br />\n如果一個人有心要扮女人<br />\n就唔會連鬚都唔剃<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/17/021131_40e4acb3a5218e443f5b471b763bd438.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F17%2F021131_40e4acb3a5218e443f5b471b763bd438.png&h=3b0e5c65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢啲擺到明戲劇效果就咪拎出黎講啦<br />\nChild登"},{"pid":"c5c68296af29176d1407899607e7e451dacea747","tid":704981,"uid":4260,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T19:01:59.000Z","msg":"連登無野多 打手同無腦細蚊仔最撚多<br />\n成2千幾個正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c820156e311f2a12fc2d9aaba7feeaba5d27a1f","tid":704981,"uid":88693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T05:44:23.000Z","msg":"呢喥有冇老鬼現場睇過張國榮演唱會？<br />\n可以比較吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6bd51352594ba1e1bfb106acdea86a72b324255","tid":704981,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T05:51:14.000Z","msg":"正皮3000 痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3771ebc3d5cf1bb62741fa47675c5b0e2fe13b56","tid":704981,"uid":1426,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T05:51:51.000Z","msg":"都係基佬"},{"pid":"87d8452f058d5f49eeeae678a8a80447e5cff01c","tid":704981,"uid":82917,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T06:01:43.000Z","msg":"個唱女性化服裝評論毀譽參半 哥哥心情惡劣<br />\n <br />\n由於張國榮演唱會造型和服裝引來不少負面新聞，哥哥（張國榮）因此心情惡劣，昨日他為港台執導禁煙宣傳短片時，在場有記者叫他一聲「哥哥」，但卻換來哥哥爆粗回應：「哥你滷味&hellip;&hellip;」。<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d54f7a7f1384a236d53